title: Video: Lana Del Rey – Carmen
content:
It’s reached the point where I’m not really sure if I’m in love with Lana Del Rey, or merely the idea of her.

Either way, there’s now no denying the impact she’s had on pop music, be it for better or worse. This new video for next single Carmen ditches the Born To Die princess-chic and reverts to Lana’s familiar ‘let’s-be-cool-and-use-vintage-looking-clips’ appeal. As you can imagine, it’s crammed with black and white clips of Grant chilling with some alternative looking dude, spliced together with retro imagery, awesome… right?
